Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.Tile

  • public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
    Each Tile has an associated type (blank or A-Z) and an assigned number of points for using it to construct a word.
    Author:
    Rajit Banerjee, 18202817, Tee Chee Guan, 18202044, Katarina Cvetkovic, 18347921 Team 15: DarkMode
